            <div type="apparatus">
               <listApp>
                   <app n="1">
                       <note>As Forsyth notes <q>The first six letters are extremely doubtful.</q> For the portion of the inscription closest to the ground, the indentations of strokes <q>can be clearly felt on the arris, but the lines are too indistinct to interpret</q> (1996, 292). From the seventh character onwards the carving is clearer and there is greater agreement amongst previous editors (ibid. 293).</note>
                   </app>
                   <app n="2">
                       <note>Rhys (1899) read:</note>
                       <rdg resp="RHY1899">
